N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4001.5 - Changes in rules

State Regulations

The commission shall promptly inform the national
organization representing State racing commissions and commissions and The

Jockey Club of all changes in the commission's rules and regulations and of all
penalties imposed. Notes
